These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, cola, 7up, hot-chocolate
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, grey, fuchsia, pink, lavender
 1. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person drinking cola##7
 3. the person drinking lemonade and the person who likes lavender have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking 7up##5
 5. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##5
 7. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes red and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 8. the person drinking milk is not the person who likes pink##6
 9. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Pet     | milk | 7up     | lemonade        | cola  | hot-chocolate          |
| Sport   | grey  | red | lavender | fuchsia | pink |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  scientist, electrician, fisherman, accountant, dressmaker
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, fantasy, western, epic, mystery
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
 2. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the fisherman and the person watching epic movies##7
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 4. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the fisherman and the person watching epic movies##7
 5. the scientist is the person watching adventure movies##1
 6. the electrician is in the middle##1
 7. the dressmaker is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 8. the scientist and the person watching fantasy movies have different parity positions##9
 9. the scientist and the person watching western movies have different parity positions##9
10. the person watching adventure movies is not to the right of the scientist##8
11. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the accountant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Food    | fisherman  | scientist | electrician  | dressmaker | accountant     |
| Hobby   | mystery | adventure   | western | epic  | fantasy |

