.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-3::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, boat, car, snowmobile
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: fantasy, western, crime, sports, family
 1. the person driving the boat is not to the left of the person watching western movies##8
 2. the person watching fantasy movies and the person driving the snowmobile have different parity positions##9
 3. the person driving the boat is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
 4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
 6. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
 7. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 8. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 9. the person driving the roller and the person watching family movies have different parity positions##9
10. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person driving the car##7
11. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
12. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |       5        |
| Beverage   | snowmobile     | car     | boat | roller | helicopter          |
| Job        | crime | fantasy | western | sports         | family |

