.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-4::.
House: tower, palace, gothic-revival, wooden, art-deco
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, peas, tomato, spinach, orange
 1. the palace house is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
 2. the person eating orange is not to the left of the palace house##8
 3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5
 4. the art-deco house is somewhere between the wooden house and the person eating tomato##7
 5. the person eating pineapple and the gothic-revival house have different parity positions##9
 6. the person eating peas is not to the left of the art-deco house##8
 7. the person eating pineapple is somewhere to the right of the person eating tomato##5
 8. the tower house is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
 9. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
10. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the wooden house##8
11. the tower house is not to the left of the person eating pineapple##8
12. the palace house is in the middle##1
13. the person eating orange is in the middle##1
14. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage   | gothic-revival    | tower  | palace | art-deco        | wooden |
| Pet        | tomato | pineapple | orange    | peas | spinach      |

