.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-20::.
There are 5 different nationalities: turkish, australian, brazilian, indian, french
5 different pets are kept: dog, lizard, mouse, horse, hedgehog
 1. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 4. the owner of the mouse and the french have the same parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the french##8
 6. the indian is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
 7. the owner of the mouse is the australian##1
 8. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 9. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
10. the french is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
11. the turkish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2     |      3      |      4      |      5      |
| Food    | australian    | indian   | turkish     | brazilian      | french   |
| Hobby   | mouse | horse | hedgehog | dog | lizard |

 